subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: María José Uribe, a 17-year-old Colombian who will be a freshman at U.C.L.A. in the fall, took advantage of a late putting lapse by Amanda Blumenherst for a 1-up victory in the match-play final of the United States Women’s Amateur Championship at Crooked Stick Golf Club in Carmel, Ind.
